Package annotool.io

Class Summary
Algorithm Represents a single algorithm(extractor, selector, classifier) loaded from the Algorithm.xml file.
AlgoXMLParser This class loads the algorithms from the xml file, parses it and creates a list of extractor, selector or classifiers that are used in GUI.
ChainIO Saves and loads the list of algorithm chains for comparison mode.
ChainModel This class is responsible for storing trained model from memory into file and loading from file into the memory.
DataInput  
DataInputDynamic Deprecated.
DataInputROI Deprecated.
DirectoryReader This is equivalent to LabelReader from target file input mode but for directory structure input mode.
ImageTargetGenerator Temporary class to generate target files for hela image set.
LabelReader Read binary labels (targets) from a file The file is formatted as below (0909080): 1st line: annotation labels, other line: target values, then file name a150 a273 1 0 k150_a150_4-23-07_L10_Sum.lsm__AJ-F__GF.tif 1 0 k150_a150_4-23-07_L11_Sum.lsm__AJ-F__GF.tif 1 0 k150_a150_4-23-07_L12_Sum.lsm__AJ-F__GF.tif 1 0 k150_a150_4-23-07_L7_Sum.lsm__AJ-F__GF.tif 1 0 k150_a150_4-23-07_L8_Sum.lsm__AJ-F__GF.tif 0 1 k150_a273_8-14-07_L10_B1_GR1_R1.lsm__AJ-F__GF.tif 0 1 k150_a273_8-14-07_L11_B1_GR1_R1.lsm__AJ-F__GF.tif 0 1 k150_a273_8-14-07_L13_B1_GR1_R1.lsm__AJ-F__GF.tif 0 1 k150_a273_8-14-07_L8_B1_GR1_R1.lsm__AJ-F__GF.tif 0 1 k150_a273_8-14-07_L9_B1_GR1_R1.lsm__AJ-F__GF.tif Added July 2011: The second line contains pairs of digital targets and the corresponding class names.
Marker3D Temporary class to mark points on 3D image.
Parameter Represents a single parameter for an algorithm.
PluginScanner This class scans the plugin folder to check for new algorithms.
ReportSaver This class is used for saving pdf report containing annotation results.
TargetFileGenerator Temporary script used for generating target file
